[ RiPPERS C0MMENT ]

Counting upwards of 14 years since the first episode of the radio
show, A State Of Trance has found a special place in the hearts of
Trance lovers and like-minded individuals. And ever since the A State
Of Trance concept was brought onto the live stage, fans have been
frantically holding their breath, eagerly awaiting the next big
event.

As A State Of Trance ventured into new territories over several
continents with a brand new musical journey called A State Of Trance
Festival, countless fans from all over the world gathered to catch a
glimpse of their favorite artists on stage. Here to once again paint
the pictures of those fantastic times: ÃƒÂ¦A State Of Trance Festival
2015'.

Some of the best records have been compiled in no less than six mixes
by six different DJs, infallibly capturing the true spirit of A State
Of Trance. Heatbeat, MaRLo, Jorn van Deynhoven, Mark Sixma, Ruben de
Ronde, and Rodg take point in providing you with their finest
records, using only their very own tracks and remixes, including
previously unreleased material. With their personal mixes, they
represent their very own style and view on Trance music, acclaimed by
fans all over the globe.

The A State Of Trance Festival 2015 compilation is exactly what
unites Trance fans all over the world. It's time to go back to the
essence.
Back to where it all started. That incredible feeling. Together in A
State Of Trance!
